WEBVTT

00:01:40.830 --> 00:01:45.950
[THE DEVIL BETWEEN US]

00:01:45.979 --> 00:01:49.000
[Episode 11]

00:02:28.560 --> 00:02:30.710
You need to know the product's features

00:02:30.710 --> 00:02:31.910
and advantages.

00:02:32.280 --> 00:02:33.600
Get it all straight,

00:02:33.870 --> 00:02:36.270
and then you'll know
the best way to sell it.

00:04:24.190 --> 00:04:25.510
I'm off to work.

00:04:26.240 --> 00:04:26.950
There's food in the kitchen.

00:04:26.950 --> 00:04:28.080
Don't forget to eat.

00:04:43.240 --> 00:04:46.860
[Good news is coming]

00:04:46.960 --> 00:04:50.250
[Nuanfeng Hengke Electronics Factory]

00:04:54.470 --> 00:04:55.630
I'm not taking the graduate entrance exam.

00:04:55.630 --> 00:04:56.750
You've been preparing for three years.

00:04:56.750 --> 00:04:57.720
Why do you want to quit?

00:04:57.720 --> 00:04:59.320
It's not that I don't want to.

00:04:59.390 --> 00:05:00.560
I just can't.

00:05:03.270 --> 00:05:04.990
Did Wang Ping really take drugs?

00:05:04.990 --> 00:05:06.820
Yes.

00:05:06.990 --> 00:05:07.600
Tell me.

00:05:07.600 --> 00:05:09.750
Why can a drug user keep her job here?

00:05:10.110 --> 00:05:12.310
What's her relationship with the boss?

00:05:14.270 --> 00:05:16.070
It's still about the drug issue.

00:05:16.390 --> 00:05:18.870
Could you please explain it to others?

00:05:19.430 --> 00:05:20.680
I heard

00:05:20.960 --> 00:05:22.620
you also took the drug, right?

00:05:22.900 --> 00:05:24.500
Is this why you came to see me?

00:05:24.520 --> 00:05:25.270
Ms. Du.

00:05:25.500 --> 00:05:27.830
I've been waiting for nearly ten minutes.

00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:30.600
Why don't you explain it

00:05:30.600 --> 00:05:31.550
to them yourself?

00:05:31.550 --> 00:05:32.700
I can help you.

00:05:32.880 --> 00:05:34.230
What is he to you?

00:05:34.350 --> 00:05:36.230
My work has nothing to do with you.

00:05:36.230 --> 00:05:37.590
Everything about you concerns me.

00:05:37.590 --> 00:05:38.300
Wang An.

00:05:39.909 --> 00:05:41.030
Where did you get this?

00:05:41.030 --> 00:05:42.030
It's not mine.

00:05:42.200 --> 00:05:43.320
I wouldn't know where to buy it
even if I wanted to.

00:05:43.320 --> 00:05:44.830
So you want to buy it, huh?

00:05:45.200 --> 00:05:46.030
Wang Ping,

00:05:46.790 --> 00:05:49.190
you said you're afraid that
I'll take drugs again.

00:05:49.190 --> 00:05:50.250
What are you doing?

00:05:50.590 --> 00:05:51.270
Let go of me!

00:05:51.470 --> 00:05:52.830
Why do I feel like
you're afraid that yourself...

00:05:52.830 --> 00:05:53.880
Enough. Stop it!

00:05:56.760 --> 00:05:58.080
You've all seen it.

00:05:59.270 --> 00:06:01.000
Recently, factory orders

00:06:01.060 --> 00:06:02.560
have dropped significantly.

00:06:02.560 --> 00:06:04.590
The leadership is very dissatisfied.

00:06:04.590 --> 00:06:05.590
Director Liu said

00:06:06.120 --> 00:06:08.470
that if the quarterly performance
of every department

00:06:08.470 --> 00:06:10.200
doesn't show a clear increase,

00:06:10.390 --> 00:06:11.560
then every single one

00:06:11.560 --> 00:06:12.830
of you here

00:06:13.520 --> 00:06:14.580
will pay the price.

00:06:14.880 --> 00:06:15.520
You'll all suffer.

00:06:15.520 --> 00:06:16.470
When you encounter difficulties,

00:06:16.470 --> 00:06:17.590
find a way to solve them.

00:06:17.590 --> 00:06:18.830
Don't pass the buck.

00:06:19.000 --> 00:06:20.230
Work together.

00:06:22.640 --> 00:06:23.000
Wang Ping.

00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:24.400
Why is she going up there?

00:06:25.080 --> 00:06:26.140
What are you doing?

00:06:32.330 --> 00:06:34.010
All of you,

00:06:35.440 --> 00:06:36.590
listen carefully.

00:06:37.390 --> 00:06:39.270
I'm not who you think I am.

00:06:41.580 --> 00:06:42.700
I did take drugs

00:06:43.390 --> 00:06:45.270
but it was by mistake.

00:06:45.710 --> 00:06:46.880
Due to that,

00:06:47.440 --> 00:06:49.240
I helped the police solve a case.

00:06:49.670 --> 00:06:51.730
Even the police didn't criticize me.

00:06:52.000 --> 00:06:55.520
What gives you the right
to gossip behind my back?

00:06:56.909 --> 00:06:57.510
Wang Ping.

00:06:57.909 --> 00:06:58.880
We're in a meeting.

00:06:58.880 --> 00:07:00.270
This isn't the proper time
to discuss your personal issues.

00:07:00.270 --> 00:07:00.790
Get down.

00:07:00.790 --> 00:07:01.350
Calm down. Come on.

00:07:01.350 --> 00:07:02.680
I'm very calm!

00:07:02.910 --> 00:07:04.230
I was so calm

00:07:04.230 --> 00:07:06.270
that you all bullied me like this.

00:07:06.560 --> 00:07:08.030
What's wrong with her?

00:07:08.230 --> 00:07:09.520
What is she doing?

00:07:10.390 --> 00:07:12.440
I've been at this factory for eight years.

00:07:12.440 --> 00:07:14.300
I've worked for you for six years.

00:07:14.680 --> 00:07:15.740
We are colleagues.

00:07:15.760 --> 00:07:16.440
Mr. Sun,

00:07:17.320 --> 00:07:19.230
I just asked you to speak the truth.

00:07:19.230 --> 00:07:20.680
Why is that so hard?

00:07:23.520 --> 00:07:24.200
Mr. Sun,

00:07:25.880 --> 00:07:28.210
you know exactly how much you skimmed off.

00:07:28.680 --> 00:07:30.520
If I get fired today,

00:07:30.520 --> 00:07:32.000
you're the first one
I'm taking down with me.

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:33.270
-Got it?
-Nonsense!

00:07:36.230 --> 00:07:37.000
Lili,

00:07:37.110 --> 00:07:38.820
have you forgotten that

00:07:38.840 --> 00:07:40.430
I taught you everything

00:07:40.460 --> 00:07:42.390
when you first joined the company?

00:07:47.560 --> 00:07:48.230
Ms. Du,

00:07:50.080 --> 00:07:51.390
that day at the copier,

00:07:52.790 --> 00:07:54.560
I waited there for ages.

00:07:54.560 --> 00:07:55.830
Didn't you see me?

00:07:57.270 --> 00:07:59.470
When your kid was sick,

00:08:00.030 --> 00:08:01.350
I covered for you during work hours,

00:08:01.350 --> 00:08:02.960
and finished the rest of your work

00:08:02.960 --> 00:08:05.080
so that you could go home early.
Have you forgotten?

00:08:05.080 --> 00:08:05.610
Sun Chao!

00:08:06.440 --> 00:08:07.770
What are you looking at?

00:08:08.270 --> 00:08:10.080
Dare you stare at me?

00:08:10.200 --> 00:08:12.560
Did you forget about your dad's accident?

00:08:12.560 --> 00:08:14.000
You don't remember anything, right?

00:08:14.000 --> 00:08:15.440
I handled your dad's affairs!

00:08:15.440 --> 00:08:17.300
I visited your mom on your behalf!

00:08:17.400 --> 00:08:18.860
Have you forgotten it all?

00:08:21.200 --> 00:08:22.460
What is wrong with you?

00:08:24.350 --> 00:08:26.640
Do you all have amnesia?

00:08:26.860 --> 00:08:28.660
Have you forgotten everything?

00:08:29.960 --> 00:08:32.070
I took those drugs by mistake.

00:08:32.070 --> 00:08:33.330
I was wrongly accused.

00:08:33.470 --> 00:08:34.630
Now you're all

00:08:34.630 --> 00:08:35.990
kicking me when I'm down, huh?

00:08:35.990 --> 00:08:37.440
You smile when you need my help,

00:08:37.440 --> 00:08:39.299
but turn your back when you don't.

00:09:12.590 --> 00:09:13.990
Hello, can I help you?

00:09:14.230 --> 00:09:15.000
How much is this?

00:09:15.000 --> 00:09:16.000
That's five yuan.

00:09:16.990 --> 00:09:18.050
Do you have gloves?

00:09:18.060 --> 00:09:18.940
This way.

00:09:20.990 --> 00:09:22.320
These are fifteen yuan.

00:09:22.530 --> 00:09:23.260
I've paid it.

00:09:23.300 --> 00:09:23.680
Okay.

00:09:26.920 --> 00:09:27.350
Sir,

00:09:27.630 --> 00:09:28.430
payment sent.

00:09:30.710 --> 00:09:32.570
How much do you want to sell it for?

00:09:33.040 --> 00:09:35.200
How much can I get if I keep the car?

00:09:36.230 --> 00:09:37.430
Ten thousand at most.

00:09:37.780 --> 00:09:38.690
I'll repay in three months.

00:09:38.690 --> 00:09:39.420
Is that okay?

00:09:41.200 --> 00:09:41.680
Okay.

00:12:34.290 --> 00:12:35.860
[Association Studio]

00:12:54.500 --> 00:12:55.940
[Dongzhang Housing Rental Registration
Form in Nuanhai Town, Nuanfeng County]

00:12:59.160 --> 00:13:00.890
Ding Lai chose a perfect place.

00:13:00.990 --> 00:13:02.790
It'll take us forever to find him

00:13:02.960 --> 00:13:04.830
in such a densely populated community.

00:13:04.830 --> 00:13:06.440
Why don't we narrow down the search area?

00:13:06.440 --> 00:13:07.110
No way.

00:13:07.110 --> 00:13:08.040
What if

00:13:08.150 --> 00:13:10.160
he's in the part we excluded?

00:13:10.680 --> 00:13:11.280
We have to search like this.

00:13:11.280 --> 00:13:12.680
We'll just take our time.

00:13:13.110 --> 00:13:14.170
Just hurry up a bit.

00:13:18.170 --> 00:13:19.020
Liu Mei...

00:13:19.160 --> 00:13:19.750
Liu Mei...

00:13:19.750 --> 00:13:21.610
Liu Mei is definitely not the one.

00:13:21.960 --> 00:13:24.470
She's my fourth uncle's younger sister.

00:13:24.950 --> 00:13:26.160
You have a lot of relatives.

00:13:26.160 --> 00:13:26.560
You have a phone call.

00:13:26.560 --> 00:13:27.620
It's a small place.

00:13:37.870 --> 00:13:38.320
Okay.

00:13:40.320 --> 00:13:41.120
Zhang Yan said

00:13:41.200 --> 00:13:42.510
Cao Jinchuan

00:13:42.510 --> 00:13:44.170
got on a bus heading to Xiamen.

00:13:44.330 --> 00:13:45.900
But he didn't get off in Xiamen.

00:13:45.900 --> 00:13:47.920
He probably got off
at a small station before that.

00:13:47.920 --> 00:13:49.560
Zhang Yan has already taken men

00:13:49.560 --> 00:13:51.220
to search station by station.

00:13:51.750 --> 00:13:53.680
As long as we don't fail
to find him like Ding Lai.

00:13:53.680 --> 00:13:55.280
Can't you be a bit more optimistic?

00:13:55.280 --> 00:13:56.610
Here you are, officers.

00:13:57.470 --> 00:13:58.080
Thanks.

00:13:58.510 --> 00:13:59.310
Okay, thanks.

00:13:59.320 --> 00:14:00.040
Thank you.

00:14:00.830 --> 00:14:01.470
Hello.

00:14:02.320 --> 00:14:03.320
We're the police.

00:14:03.470 --> 00:14:03.870
Sir.

00:14:03.870 --> 00:14:04.470
Let me ask you something.

00:14:04.470 --> 00:14:05.930
Have you seen this person?

00:14:06.440 --> 00:14:06.990
No.

00:14:06.990 --> 00:14:07.510
Hello.

00:14:07.680 --> 00:14:08.390
We're the police.

00:14:08.390 --> 00:14:09.230
Let me ask you something.

00:14:09.230 --> 00:14:10.690
Have you seen this person?

00:14:10.960 --> 00:14:11.710
No.

00:14:12.110 --> 00:14:12.920
Are you sure?

00:14:13.160 --> 00:14:13.870
No.

00:14:13.920 --> 00:14:14.650
Are you sure?

00:14:16.160 --> 00:14:17.040
Let me ask you.

00:14:17.440 --> 00:14:19.590
Why did you suddenly buy

00:14:19.590 --> 00:14:20.710
that delivery box?

00:14:21.530 --> 00:14:22.740
I do renovations.

00:14:23.110 --> 00:14:24.590
I use it to pack lunches

00:14:24.590 --> 00:14:25.850
for the guys at my site.

00:14:25.960 --> 00:14:26.820
It works great.

00:14:26.870 --> 00:14:28.320
How is it working for you?

00:14:29.110 --> 00:14:29.920
No way.

00:14:30.200 --> 00:14:31.110
I used it for a week straight,

00:14:31.110 --> 00:14:32.390
and my skin was smooth and fair.

00:14:32.390 --> 00:14:33.110
Really.

00:14:33.470 --> 00:14:34.930
Why don't you try it again?

00:14:36.330 --> 00:14:37.630
Alright.

00:14:37.750 --> 00:14:38.110
Okay.

00:14:38.470 --> 00:14:40.870
I'll contact you
when we have new products.

00:14:43.320 --> 00:14:44.160
Ms. Liu.

00:14:45.080 --> 00:14:46.080
How is it?

00:14:46.080 --> 00:14:46.960
You said that your skin

00:14:46.960 --> 00:14:48.470
was a bit sensitive.

00:14:49.510 --> 00:14:51.040
It should be perfect for you.

00:14:51.040 --> 00:14:51.770
It's no good?

00:14:52.020 --> 00:14:52.500
It's okay.

00:14:52.500 --> 00:14:53.870
I'll send you some more later.

00:14:53.870 --> 00:14:55.000
You can try it again.

00:14:55.230 --> 00:14:55.750
Okay.

00:14:56.630 --> 00:14:57.680
No rush to order.

00:14:57.830 --> 00:14:58.400
Alright.

00:14:59.200 --> 00:15:00.280
Still no buyers?

00:15:01.160 --> 00:15:02.440
What's going on?

00:15:02.440 --> 00:15:03.460
It's sold well

00:15:03.480 --> 00:15:04.750
in Hainan.

00:15:07.400 --> 00:15:09.000
Could you have been scammed?

00:15:09.620 --> 00:15:11.470
Is that sales data reliable?

00:15:12.280 --> 00:15:13.610
Why are you so annoying?

00:15:14.230 --> 00:15:15.920
I've always hated this about you.

00:15:15.920 --> 00:15:17.510
You can't help with anything

00:15:17.510 --> 00:15:18.470
but make snide remarks

00:15:18.470 --> 00:15:19.670
to make things worse.

00:15:20.320 --> 00:15:21.990
You're getting carried away again

00:15:21.990 --> 00:15:24.200
since you are living a happy life, right?

00:15:24.200 --> 00:15:25.390
Okay, okay, I am sorry.

00:15:25.390 --> 00:15:26.320
I'll shut up.

00:15:32.990 --> 00:15:34.160
I figure there is something

00:15:34.160 --> 00:15:35.780
wrong with my mindset right now.

00:15:35.780 --> 00:15:37.970
I can't focus on the business at all.

00:15:39.400 --> 00:15:41.430
I'm worried about everything all day.

00:15:41.430 --> 00:15:42.960
When Hu Wenjing came over the other day,

00:15:42.960 --> 00:15:44.800
I was a nervous wreck.

00:15:45.710 --> 00:15:46.630
I'm on edge all day.

00:15:46.630 --> 00:15:47.920
How can I do business

00:15:48.400 --> 00:15:49.460
and sell anything?

00:15:49.750 --> 00:15:51.080
We can't go on like this.

00:15:56.750 --> 00:15:57.610
How about this?

00:15:58.080 --> 00:15:59.440
Call Hu Wenjing.

00:16:00.780 --> 00:16:02.310
Invite her over for dinner.

00:16:03.470 --> 00:16:04.600
We'll set the stage,

00:16:05.510 --> 00:16:07.680
saying we got divorced recently,

00:16:08.630 --> 00:16:09.810
but I keep coming back

00:16:09.810 --> 00:16:10.940
to pester you.

00:16:12.510 --> 00:16:14.470
That way, Hu Wenjing might not suspect

00:16:14.470 --> 00:16:15.960
that Ding Lai is here.

00:16:22.680 --> 00:16:23.540
Will that work?

00:16:24.960 --> 00:16:26.110
I need to ask you about someone.

00:16:26.110 --> 00:16:27.510
Does he look familiar?

00:16:29.080 --> 00:16:29.940
Never seen him.

00:16:29.960 --> 00:16:31.200
Do you live alone?

00:16:31.630 --> 00:16:32.230
Yes.

00:16:33.160 --> 00:16:34.280
Where is your husband?

00:16:34.280 --> 00:16:35.560
He works at a factory.

00:16:37.590 --> 00:16:39.120
How often does he come back?

00:16:39.200 --> 00:16:41.560
Usually, only
during the Chinese New Year holiday.

00:16:41.560 --> 00:16:43.890
Only during the Chinese New Year holiday?

00:16:45.470 --> 00:16:48.040
Do you interact much with your neighbors?

00:16:48.920 --> 00:16:49.590
Just so-so.

00:16:49.800 --> 00:16:50.470
Okay.

00:16:51.950 --> 00:16:53.150
Sorry to disturb you.

00:16:53.350 --> 00:16:54.990
If you see any strangers

00:16:55.160 --> 00:16:56.400
or anyone suspicious,

00:16:56.400 --> 00:16:57.570
give us a call.

00:16:57.570 --> 00:16:58.960
[Investigating nearby? Come to my home
for lunch. Don't refuse. Food is ready.]

00:16:58.960 --> 00:16:59.540
Okay.

00:17:02.380 --> 00:17:02.750
Okay.

00:17:02.750 --> 00:17:05.030
Can my colleague join us?

00:17:06.650 --> 00:17:07.710
Come on in.

00:17:08.030 --> 00:17:08.550
Come on.

00:17:09.440 --> 00:17:10.270
Are you

00:17:10.270 --> 00:17:10.990
Jin,

00:17:11.160 --> 00:17:11.790
or Long?

00:17:11.790 --> 00:17:12.510
Jin Longzheng.

00:17:12.510 --> 00:17:13.069
Jin Longzheng.

00:17:13.069 --> 00:17:14.400
Long, come on in.

00:17:14.550 --> 00:17:15.410
Close the door.

00:17:15.599 --> 00:17:16.030
Okay.

00:17:16.960 --> 00:17:17.790
You're here.

00:17:17.790 --> 00:17:18.650
Wenjing is here.

00:17:18.650 --> 00:17:19.609
Have a seat.

00:17:20.030 --> 00:17:21.270
You two...

00:17:21.270 --> 00:17:22.800
Xiaoya will tell you later.

00:17:22.920 --> 00:17:23.270
Have a seat first.

00:17:23.270 --> 00:17:24.160
This is...

00:17:24.160 --> 00:17:24.920
My colleague.

00:17:24.920 --> 00:17:25.550
Yes, colleague.

00:17:25.550 --> 00:17:26.440
You can call me Jin Longzheng.

00:17:26.440 --> 00:17:27.030
Officer Jin.

00:17:27.030 --> 00:17:28.030
Have a seat.

00:17:28.030 --> 00:17:29.160
The soup is almost ready.

00:17:29.160 --> 00:17:29.790
Jin, right?

00:17:29.790 --> 00:17:30.510
Come sit here.

00:17:30.510 --> 00:17:31.270
Okay.

00:17:32.390 --> 00:17:32.990
Well.

00:17:34.960 --> 00:17:35.680
Yes.

00:17:40.080 --> 00:17:42.410
Cheng Xiaodong, your cooking is amazing.

00:17:42.670 --> 00:17:44.000
Bian will be pissed off.

00:17:44.270 --> 00:17:45.230
It's really delicious.

00:17:45.230 --> 00:17:46.030
Not bad, right?

00:17:46.030 --> 00:17:46.960
It's delicious.

00:17:47.450 --> 00:17:49.310
It's all thanks to Xiaoya's guidance.

00:17:49.310 --> 00:17:50.170
Come on, Honey.

00:17:50.400 --> 00:17:51.730
Have some winter melon.

00:17:54.550 --> 00:17:55.480
Put it here.

00:17:56.920 --> 00:17:58.550
Why don't you two just remarry?

00:17:58.550 --> 00:17:59.990
Stop going back and forth.

00:17:59.990 --> 00:18:01.160
It's exhausting

00:18:01.160 --> 00:18:02.030
and costly.

00:18:02.120 --> 00:18:03.070
No way.

00:18:03.160 --> 00:18:04.680
He's still on probation.

00:18:04.680 --> 00:18:05.300
Right?

00:18:05.470 --> 00:18:06.360
Yes.

00:18:06.910 --> 00:18:07.770
Do you remember

00:18:07.780 --> 00:18:08.750
the last time

00:18:09.250 --> 00:18:10.300
he cursed me on the street?

00:18:10.300 --> 00:18:11.700
Didn't you curse him too?

00:18:12.360 --> 00:18:12.990
I don't care.

00:18:12.990 --> 00:18:14.050
He cursed me first.

00:18:14.470 --> 00:18:15.440
Since then,

00:18:15.790 --> 00:18:17.270
he's turned over a new leaf.

00:18:17.270 --> 00:18:18.470
He treats me well now,

00:18:18.600 --> 00:18:20.120
coming over every day
to help with shipping,

00:18:20.120 --> 00:18:20.990
cooking,

00:18:21.280 --> 00:18:22.740
and taking good care of me.

00:18:23.710 --> 00:18:24.550
But honestly,

00:18:25.140 --> 00:18:27.160
your cooking is much better
than your mom's.

00:18:27.160 --> 00:18:27.920
You're absolutely right, Honey.

00:18:27.920 --> 00:18:28.680
Eat more.

00:18:28.680 --> 00:18:30.550
You're really not good at sweet talk.

00:18:30.550 --> 00:18:31.400
Give me a piece of meat.

00:18:31.400 --> 00:18:32.130
Here you are.

00:18:33.270 --> 00:18:34.990
Are you patrolling nearby?

00:18:35.200 --> 00:18:36.330
You got here so fast.

00:18:36.400 --> 00:18:38.030
I happened to be checking
the building next door.

00:18:38.030 --> 00:18:39.030
When I saw your message,

00:18:39.030 --> 00:18:40.440
I was just about to head this way.

00:18:40.440 --> 00:18:41.270
No wonder

00:18:41.460 --> 00:18:43.520
you reached the staircase in no time.

00:18:45.550 --> 00:18:46.360
I'm going to the restroom.

00:18:46.360 --> 00:18:47.270
Go ahead.

00:18:47.270 --> 00:18:48.030
It's by the light.

00:18:48.030 --> 00:18:48.400
Okay.

00:18:48.400 --> 00:18:49.130
By the light.

00:18:49.400 --> 00:18:50.200
Behind the door.

00:18:50.200 --> 00:18:50.960
I see it.

00:18:53.640 --> 00:18:54.400
Eat more,

00:18:54.750 --> 00:18:55.400
Long.

00:18:55.400 --> 00:18:56.680
-Jin Long.
-I've been eating.

00:18:56.680 --> 00:18:57.680
Come on, eat this.

00:19:41.200 --> 00:19:43.310
Let's call Wang Ping
and go singing tonight together.

00:19:43.310 --> 00:19:45.070
Do you think I'm that carefree?

00:19:45.070 --> 00:19:46.200
I work like a dog all day.

00:19:46.200 --> 00:19:47.400
I have no spare time to go singing.

00:19:47.400 --> 00:19:48.070
Just head back.

00:19:48.070 --> 00:19:48.400
Let's go.

00:19:48.400 --> 00:19:49.440
Don't just focus on work.

00:19:49.440 --> 00:19:50.200
Take care of yourself.

00:19:50.200 --> 00:19:50.840
Wear more clothes.

00:19:50.840 --> 00:19:52.440
Or you'll get arthritis when you're old.

00:19:52.440 --> 00:19:53.200
Big Eyes.

00:19:53.470 --> 00:19:54.470
Take good care of Wenjing for me.

00:19:54.470 --> 00:19:54.920
Okay.

00:19:54.920 --> 00:19:55.200
Bye.

00:19:55.200 --> 00:19:55.920
Come visit when you're free.

00:19:55.920 --> 00:19:56.200
Okay.

00:19:56.200 --> 00:19:56.920
Take care.

00:19:57.300 --> 00:19:58.170
Take care, Officer Jin.

00:19:58.170 --> 00:19:58.640
Okay.

00:19:58.640 --> 00:19:59.160
Bye.

00:19:59.400 --> 00:19:59.920
Bye.

00:20:06.880 --> 00:20:07.800
Stop acting.

00:20:16.880 --> 00:20:17.680
Give me a pen.

00:20:22.400 --> 00:20:23.990
She was kind enough
to treat you to a meal

00:20:23.990 --> 00:20:25.120
but you suspect her?

00:20:25.830 --> 00:20:27.750
[Ya]

00:20:27.920 --> 00:20:28.640
Don't say that.

00:20:28.640 --> 00:20:31.640
I don't feel good about
suspecting my friend, either.

00:20:31.750 --> 00:20:33.310
It's okay if she hadn't invited
me to dinner.

00:20:33.310 --> 00:20:35.510
But now, I feel like something's wrong.

00:20:37.680 --> 00:20:38.940
Did you find anything?

00:20:40.680 --> 00:20:42.280
I know Li Xiaoya pretty well.

00:20:43.030 --> 00:20:44.710
She's very decisive.

00:20:45.270 --> 00:20:47.550
Now that she finally managed
to divorce Cheng Xiaodong,

00:20:47.550 --> 00:20:49.160
I don't believe she still

00:20:49.160 --> 00:20:50.530
has lingering feelings for him

00:20:50.530 --> 00:20:52.660
or misses his cooking.

00:20:53.790 --> 00:20:55.070
Something feels off.

00:20:55.710 --> 00:20:57.940
They just got divorced.

00:20:59.070 --> 00:21:01.030
One only cherishes things
after he or she loses them.

00:21:01.030 --> 00:21:03.120
It's reasonable to regret it and remarry.

00:21:03.120 --> 00:21:04.850
Aren't you a bit too sensitive?

00:21:05.360 --> 00:21:07.020
When I went to their bathroom,

00:21:07.640 --> 00:21:08.640
I saw two toothbrushes.

00:21:08.640 --> 00:21:10.120
One of them was brand new,

00:21:10.120 --> 00:21:11.120
just opened,

00:21:11.120 --> 00:21:13.580
unlike the other one,
which had signs of use.

00:21:13.920 --> 00:21:14.990
Maybe

00:21:14.990 --> 00:21:16.710
she just replaced one.

00:21:17.710 --> 00:21:18.960
What exactly do you suspect them of?

00:21:18.960 --> 00:21:21.990
Do you suspect they are
accomplices of Ding Lai?

00:21:22.710 --> 00:21:23.550
Is that possible?

00:21:23.550 --> 00:21:25.150
He kept getting deliveries.

00:21:25.710 --> 00:21:26.750
Anyway,

00:21:27.510 --> 00:21:28.750
it'll be great if there's nothing
wrong with them

00:21:28.750 --> 00:21:30.360
after the investigation result
is released.

00:21:30.360 --> 00:21:31.620
Where is the next stop?

00:21:31.990 --> 00:21:32.880
Next stop

00:21:33.230 --> 00:21:34.470
is Liu Lijun's home.

00:21:34.470 --> 00:21:35.070
Liu...

00:21:35.200 --> 00:21:36.680
Liu Lijun's home isn't that way.

00:21:36.680 --> 00:21:37.470
It's over there.

00:21:37.470 --> 00:21:39.270
I'm just accompanying you for rehab?

00:21:39.270 --> 00:21:40.230
Liu Lijun's is the one on the right.

00:21:40.230 --> 00:21:41.310
Yes, to the right.

00:21:45.070 --> 00:21:47.270
Do you think Hu Wenjing will believe it?

00:21:52.960 --> 00:21:53.710
Hard to say.

00:22:09.550 --> 00:22:10.160
It's from Ken.

00:22:10.160 --> 00:22:11.030
You talk to him.

00:22:11.030 --> 00:22:13.030
He's probably asking about
the house in the countryside.

00:22:13.030 --> 00:22:13.960
I'll talk to him.

00:22:21.640 --> 00:22:22.230
Ken.

00:22:23.990 --> 00:22:25.120
Xiaoya is out.

00:22:25.990 --> 00:22:27.360
Tell me if there's anything.

00:22:27.360 --> 00:22:29.160
I'll tell her when she gets back.

00:22:29.840 --> 00:22:30.770
What did you say?

00:22:33.070 --> 00:22:33.870
Okay, I got it.

00:22:37.920 --> 00:22:39.320
Cheng Ken said he has a big business

00:22:39.320 --> 00:22:40.050
to talk to us.

00:22:41.360 --> 00:22:42.160
Big business?

00:22:42.600 --> 00:22:44.230
What big business could he have?

00:22:44.230 --> 00:22:45.230
You go talk to him.

00:22:46.310 --> 00:22:47.310
Just say I'm busy.

00:22:48.370 --> 00:22:49.970
Okay, I'll go see him in a bit.

00:22:58.680 --> 00:22:59.270
Coming.

00:23:03.440 --> 00:23:03.960
Come in.

00:23:04.710 --> 00:23:05.640
Where is Xiaoya?

00:23:05.840 --> 00:23:06.960
She's sorting goods at home.

00:23:06.960 --> 00:23:08.820
You can discuss anything with me.

00:23:09.160 --> 00:23:11.560
Can you call the shots
on business matters?

00:23:16.310 --> 00:23:17.240
Where is Jiajia?

00:23:17.510 --> 00:23:18.160
Jiajia!

00:23:19.120 --> 00:23:19.400
Jia!

00:23:19.400 --> 00:23:19.990
Coming.

00:23:19.990 --> 00:23:20.680
Look.

00:23:20.990 --> 00:23:21.470
Uncle.

00:23:21.470 --> 00:23:22.510
Jiajia.

00:23:23.600 --> 00:23:24.510
Did you miss me?

00:23:24.510 --> 00:23:25.470
Yes.

00:23:25.470 --> 00:23:26.600
I knew you missed me.

00:23:27.120 --> 00:23:28.580
I brought you some snacks.

00:23:28.750 --> 00:23:30.120
So many.

00:23:30.230 --> 00:23:30.830
Come here.

00:23:31.470 --> 00:23:32.470
How are you going?

00:23:33.440 --> 00:23:35.120
Enjoy every day as it comes.

00:23:35.960 --> 00:23:37.920
That's getting profound.

00:23:38.160 --> 00:23:38.990
Did your dad teach you that?

00:23:38.990 --> 00:23:40.250
I can't teach her that.

00:23:40.310 --> 00:23:42.370
She comes up with new words every day.

00:23:42.640 --> 00:23:43.030
Where did

00:23:43.030 --> 00:23:43.960
you learn that?

00:23:44.200 --> 00:23:44.960
The internet.

00:23:44.960 --> 00:23:45.920
The internet.

00:23:46.550 --> 00:23:46.960
Jiajia.

00:23:46.960 --> 00:23:47.960
When you recover,

00:23:48.030 --> 00:23:49.230
go back to school and crush them.

00:23:49.230 --> 00:23:49.710
Okay?

00:23:49.710 --> 00:23:50.200
Okay.

00:23:51.990 --> 00:23:52.360
Go.

00:23:52.360 --> 00:23:52.840
Go eat.

00:23:56.600 --> 00:23:57.120
Go play for a bit.

00:23:57.120 --> 00:23:58.650
I need to talk to your uncle.

00:24:00.750 --> 00:24:02.160
So mysterious.

00:24:08.030 --> 00:24:08.710
Ken,

00:24:09.990 --> 00:24:11.990
why are you so happy lately?

00:24:18.100 --> 00:24:20.640
My mind

00:24:23.600 --> 00:24:24.330
is clear now.

00:24:25.990 --> 00:24:28.650
I've figured something out
these past few days.

00:24:30.030 --> 00:24:30.960
The root cause

00:24:31.230 --> 00:24:32.640
of my suffering

00:24:33.790 --> 00:24:34.990
was the lack of money.

00:24:36.440 --> 00:24:37.680
Being poor made me miserable,

00:24:37.680 --> 00:24:38.610
very miserable.

00:24:38.790 --> 00:24:39.680
But luckily,

00:24:40.570 --> 00:24:42.140
God bless me.

00:24:43.600 --> 00:24:44.730
He left a path for me,

00:24:45.270 --> 00:24:47.230
a path to get rich.

00:24:47.750 --> 00:24:49.120
Good.

00:24:49.120 --> 00:24:50.120
I'm happy for you.

00:24:51.270 --> 00:24:51.920
What?

00:24:52.300 --> 00:24:53.070
Just happy?

00:24:53.070 --> 00:24:54.550
Won't you even ask what path it is?

00:24:54.550 --> 00:24:55.750
I don't care about money.

00:24:55.750 --> 00:24:56.920
It's good that you get rich.

00:24:56.920 --> 00:24:58.320
No need to worry about me.

00:25:01.510 --> 00:25:02.200
Right.

00:25:02.960 --> 00:25:03.400
Right.

00:25:03.920 --> 00:25:05.450
You don't care about money.

00:25:06.640 --> 00:25:07.840
What about Li Xiaoya?

00:25:08.960 --> 00:25:10.620
Doesn't she care about money?

00:25:12.790 --> 00:25:13.990
Be straightforward.

00:25:16.270 --> 00:25:17.030
Look.

00:25:17.660 --> 00:25:19.720
Notice anything different about me?

00:25:27.680 --> 00:25:29.140
Did you lose weight again?

00:25:35.940 --> 00:25:37.510
I lost 2.5 kilograms in three days.

00:25:37.510 --> 00:25:39.110
2.5 kilograms in three days?

00:25:39.360 --> 00:25:40.440
What did you eat?

00:25:43.270 --> 00:25:44.790
I ate a little bit.

00:25:44.790 --> 00:25:45.790
Very little.

00:25:45.920 --> 00:25:46.550
Very little.

00:25:46.550 --> 00:25:48.480
But mainly, I've been taking this.

00:25:48.840 --> 00:25:50.100
Physically, I'm fine.

00:25:50.230 --> 00:25:51.430
Mentally, I'm great.

00:25:51.680 --> 00:25:52.940
I'm excited, or hyper.

00:25:53.120 --> 00:25:54.320
I have nothing wrong.

00:25:57.790 --> 00:25:59.320
I don't feel hungry either.

00:25:59.880 --> 00:26:01.080
Interesting, right?

00:26:01.600 --> 00:26:02.130
Interesting.

00:26:02.130 --> 00:26:03.460
Three days on just this?

00:26:05.310 --> 00:26:06.110
Milk tablets?

00:26:06.470 --> 00:26:07.160
Homemade?

00:26:08.550 --> 00:26:09.200
Let me try one.

00:26:09.200 --> 00:26:09.920
Don't.

00:26:16.030 --> 00:26:17.290
It's not a milk tablet.

00:26:18.460 --> 00:26:19.790
It's the best diet pill.

00:26:26.750 --> 00:26:27.880
I've been thinking.

00:26:29.920 --> 00:26:30.790
Li Xiaoya

00:26:31.200 --> 00:26:32.330
has so many clients.

00:26:32.550 --> 00:26:34.390
Most of them are

00:26:34.990 --> 00:26:35.720
young girls.

00:26:36.920 --> 00:26:38.560
They all want to lose weight.

00:26:40.120 --> 00:26:42.650
It helped me lose
2.5 kilograms in three days.

00:26:43.070 --> 00:26:43.840
Tell me,

00:26:45.030 --> 00:26:46.760
how much money could this make?

00:26:55.880 --> 00:26:57.540
Did you add something to this?

00:27:03.920 --> 00:27:04.600
Hungry.

00:27:04.860 --> 00:27:06.070
I'm hungry.

00:27:07.510 --> 00:27:08.170
Who is that?

00:27:11.120 --> 00:27:11.880
Quiet!

00:27:13.030 --> 00:27:14.660
I'm hungry.

00:27:37.370 --> 00:27:38.100
You're back.

00:27:48.200 --> 00:27:49.550
What happened to you?

00:27:50.490 --> 00:27:52.350
You look like you've seen a ghost.

00:27:58.270 --> 00:27:59.790
Don't lend the countryside house

00:27:59.790 --> 00:28:00.680
to Cheng Ken.

00:28:01.600 --> 00:28:02.800
If he calls you again,

00:28:03.030 --> 00:28:04.030
don't answer.

00:28:05.160 --> 00:28:05.920
Why?

00:28:06.990 --> 00:28:07.710
Just don't.

00:28:10.680 --> 00:28:11.810
What did he tell you?

00:28:12.840 --> 00:28:13.600
Nothing.

00:28:15.200 --> 00:28:16.130
Cheng Xiaodong.

00:28:16.510 --> 00:28:17.710
Didn't we agree?

00:28:18.470 --> 00:28:20.270
You can't keep anything from me.

00:28:39.710 --> 00:28:42.310
You said the police are looking
for a man and a woman

00:28:42.310 --> 00:28:43.570
and showed you photos.

00:28:44.360 --> 00:28:45.640
The man is Cheng Ken.

00:28:47.030 --> 00:28:47.710
The woman

00:28:48.300 --> 00:28:50.830
is the girl he said
to send to the countryside.

00:28:55.660 --> 00:28:57.310
The person Hu Wenjing is looking for

00:28:57.310 --> 00:28:58.510
is Cheng Ken?

00:29:00.230 --> 00:29:01.200
Your brother is

00:29:02.070 --> 00:29:03.160
a drug dealer?

00:29:05.440 --> 00:29:06.810
Are you kidding?

00:29:06.990 --> 00:29:08.850
Ken is too much of a loser for that.

00:29:13.200 --> 00:29:14.960
And it's all a coincidence.

00:29:15.790 --> 00:29:16.840
Cheng Ken

00:29:17.510 --> 00:29:19.840
wanted to buy a kidney
on the black market.

00:29:20.030 --> 00:29:21.830
But he got scammed by the seller.

00:29:22.360 --> 00:29:23.960
The seller didn't give Ken a kidney,

00:29:23.960 --> 00:29:25.560
but a living person instead.

00:29:25.870 --> 00:29:26.440
That is

00:29:26.440 --> 00:29:27.700
the girl he mentioned,

00:29:28.510 --> 00:29:30.440
who has mental issues.

00:29:31.710 --> 00:29:33.640
Then, he couldn't find the seller.

00:29:33.740 --> 00:29:35.310
So, Ken took the girl home.

00:29:35.730 --> 00:29:36.760
Unexpectedly, that girl

00:29:36.760 --> 00:29:38.420
pooped out drugs at his place.

00:29:47.400 --> 00:29:48.070
So,

00:29:51.800 --> 00:29:54.660
does Ken know about
our relationship with Ding Lai?

00:29:55.880 --> 00:29:57.880
How did he dare tell you this?

00:29:58.960 --> 00:29:59.960
He had no choice.

00:30:01.600 --> 00:30:03.600
He originally planned to sell these drugs

00:30:03.600 --> 00:30:04.710
to drug dealers,

00:30:05.080 --> 00:30:05.920
but failed.

00:30:06.680 --> 00:30:07.680
So he tried

00:30:08.080 --> 00:30:09.800
to sell them himself.

00:30:10.310 --> 00:30:11.230
You told him

00:30:11.380 --> 00:30:12.710
your clients

00:30:12.710 --> 00:30:13.960
are all young girls.

00:30:14.510 --> 00:30:17.070
He wanted to package
the drugs as diet pills

00:30:17.150 --> 00:30:18.910
and let you sell them.

00:30:19.120 --> 00:30:21.430
To figure out the properties of the drugs,

00:30:21.430 --> 00:30:23.160
he started using them himself.

00:30:23.550 --> 00:30:24.910
And I think, after using drugs,

00:30:24.910 --> 00:30:26.390
he has lost his mind.

00:30:26.640 --> 00:30:27.710
He wants to drag us

00:30:27.710 --> 00:30:29.310
into dealing drugs with him.

00:30:31.640 --> 00:30:33.440
One gram sells for 500,000 yuan.

00:30:33.820 --> 00:30:35.220
That day at Black Forest,

00:30:35.470 --> 00:30:36.670
how many did you want?

00:30:37.030 --> 00:30:38.070
450 grams.

00:30:38.440 --> 00:30:39.230
450 grams.

00:30:41.910 --> 00:30:43.570
That's over 100 million yuan.

00:30:48.650 --> 00:30:50.880
Does Ken have all of Ding Lai's drugs?

00:30:52.980 --> 00:30:54.640
That's a huge amount of money.

00:31:01.960 --> 00:31:02.840
We've solved

00:31:03.510 --> 00:31:04.680
Ding Lai's issue.

00:31:05.710 --> 00:31:07.400
As long as there's no evidence,

00:31:07.400 --> 00:31:08.860
the police can't touch us.

00:31:09.480 --> 00:31:12.000
But drug dealing is an ongoing activity.

00:31:12.710 --> 00:31:14.570
There are loopholes everywhere.

00:31:14.640 --> 00:31:15.790
We don't have an organization,

00:31:15.790 --> 00:31:17.250
and no one to take the fall.

00:31:17.270 --> 00:31:18.620
Once the police target us,

00:31:18.620 --> 00:31:19.970
we're doomed.

00:31:24.310 --> 00:31:25.640
I was not going to deal drugs.

00:31:25.640 --> 00:31:27.440
Why are you getting so worked up?

00:31:28.840 --> 00:31:30.710
The most addictive drug is money.

00:31:32.230 --> 00:31:33.760
You're already in too deep.

00:31:34.230 --> 00:31:36.290
Don't risk your life for money again.

00:31:36.510 --> 00:31:37.880
Then I've been addicted for a long time.

00:31:37.880 --> 00:31:40.080
I won't be able to quit in this lifetime.

00:31:49.750 --> 00:31:50.480
Are you done?

00:31:50.510 --> 00:31:52.240
Hu Wenjing is rushing us again.

00:31:54.230 --> 00:31:55.380
Done.

00:31:56.230 --> 00:31:58.990
She always rushes us
like it's a matter of life and death.

00:31:58.990 --> 00:31:59.750
In your team,

00:31:59.750 --> 00:32:01.180
she's the one I'm most afraid of.

00:32:01.180 --> 00:32:02.120
Even I'm afraid of her.

00:32:02.120 --> 00:32:03.650
See? She's even rushing me.

00:32:05.930 --> 00:32:07.390
Thanks for your hard work.

00:32:07.640 --> 00:32:08.970
It's just my lot in life.

00:32:11.070 --> 00:32:12.920
The people in Nuanfeng
are certainly enthusiastic.

00:32:12.920 --> 00:32:14.780
They've given us plenty of leads.

00:32:14.840 --> 00:32:16.700
But not a single one was accurate.

00:32:17.460 --> 00:32:19.590
What should we say to Captain Wu later?

00:32:21.840 --> 00:32:22.960
Tell him the truth.

00:32:23.120 --> 00:32:25.680
We haven't found any solid evidence.

00:32:26.920 --> 00:32:28.720
But we're following up on leads.

00:32:29.120 --> 00:32:30.680
That's all we can say.

00:32:39.680 --> 00:32:40.480
Director Dai.

00:32:40.920 --> 00:32:42.790
None of the hair samples you sent

00:32:43.200 --> 00:32:44.750
belong to Ding Lai.

00:32:46.400 --> 00:32:47.460
Alright.

00:32:47.680 --> 00:32:48.310
Got it.

00:32:55.030 --> 00:32:56.070
Impossible.

00:32:57.120 --> 00:32:58.200
I've been in contact with him.

00:32:58.200 --> 00:33:00.130
Everything was okay a few days ago.

00:33:04.350 --> 00:33:05.180
Fine.

00:33:05.790 --> 00:33:06.550
